{

	103_63: {
		cardInfo: {
			//id: 103_63.1
			parent: 103_63
			variant: ERRATA
			variantPath: errata/pc
			revision: 1
			image: sets/V3/LOTR-ENV3S063.1_card.jpg
			collInfo: V3_63
			rarity: _
		}
		title: Cirith Ungol Watcher
		subtitle: Spirit of Vigilance
		unique: 2
		side: Shadow
		culture: Wraith
		twilight: 2
		type: Artifact
		target: self
		keywords: Support Area
		effects: [
			{
				type: ExtraCost
				cost: {
					type: Spot
					filter: ringwraith
				}
			}
			{
				type: trigger
				optional: false
				trigger: {
					type: Exerted
					filter: companion
				}
				requires: {
					type: perPhaseLimit
					phase: regroup
					limit: 1
				}
				effect: [
					{
						type: incrementPerPhaseLimit
						phase: regroup
						limit: 1
					}
					{
						type: DrawCards
						count: 1
					}
				]
			}
			{
				type: Response
				trigger: {
					type: Exerted
					filter: companion
					source: side(freeps)
					memorize: exertedComp
				}
				cost: {
					type: Discard
					select: choose(another,title(Cirith Ungol Watcher))
				}
				effect: [
					{
						type: AddTwilight
						amount: 4
					}
					{
						type: Hinder
						select: memory(exertedComp)
					}
				]
			}
		]
		gametext: To play, spot a [ringwraith] card.<br>Each time a companion exerts, draw a card (limit once per site).<br>Response: If a companion is exerted by a Free Peoples card, discard another Cirith Ungol Watcher to add (4) and hinder that companion.
		lore: ""
		promotext: ""
		alts: {
			promos: {
			}
			errata: {
			}
		}
	}

	103_67: {
		cardInfo: {
			//id: 103_67.1
			parent: 103_67
			variant: ERRATA
			variantPath: errata/pc
			revision: 1
			image: sets/V3/LOTR-ENV3S067.1_card.jpg
			collInfo: V3_67
			rarity: _
		}
		title: Ill Wind
		unique: true
		side: Shadow
		culture: Wraith
		twilight: 1
		type: Condition
		target: self
		keywords: Support Area
		effects: [
			{
				type: Trigger
				optional: true
				trigger: {
					type: Played
					filter: Nazgul
					player: you
				}
				requires: {
					type: playedCardThisPhase
					filter: Nazgul
					min: 2
					max: 2
				}
				effect: {
					type: preventable
					text: Would you like to exert another companion to prevent hindering a wounded companion (or wound if The Witch-king can be spotted)?
					player: freeps
					cost: {
						type: Exert
						player: freeps
						select: choose(another,companion)
					}
					effect: [
						{
							type: ChooseActiveCards
							text: Select a wounded companion to hinder
							select: choose(wounded,companion)
							memorize: chosenComp
						}
						{
							type: If
							check: {
								type: CanSpot
								filter: title(The Witch-king)
							}
							true: {
								type: Wound
								select: memory(chosenComp)
							}
							false: {
								type: Exert
								select: memory(chosenComp)
							}
						}
						{
							type: Hinder
							select: memory(chosenComp)
						}
					]
				}
			}
		]
		gametext: The second time you play a Nazgul each Shadow phase, you may hinder a wounded companion.  The Free Peoples player may make you exert another companion to prevent this (or wound if you can spot The Witch-king).
		lore: "'Alas! For she was pitted against a foe beyond the strength of her mind or body.'"
		promotext: ""
		alts: {
			promos: {
			}
			errata: {
			}
		}
	}

